▐█▌      ·PLOT·                                                              ▐█▌
▐█▌                                                                          ▐█▌
▐█▌      Frank Keller is a New York detective investigating a case of a      ▐█▌
▐█▌      serial killer who finds the victims through the lonely hearts       ▐█▌
▐▓▌      column in newspapers. Keller falls in love with Helen, the main     ▐▓▌
▐▓▌      suspect in the case.                                                ▐▓▌
